---------
						CHUONG 1 : GIOI THIEU
- Nhat muon lam may tinh the he thu 4, ko lap trinh chi noi , tiep xuc truc tiep.
- Nghien cuu ngu nghia, cac tu ket hop ra 1 nghia dung ko phai nhi sau
- Ex:  I saw the man who saw the wood by saw.
- Chuong 3: bai tap phan tich theo bieu do 
- Tam ly cung anh huong den ngu nghia, hoan canh.
- Tritology
- xet den nhung vung may tinh co the thuc thie, tren text, dialogue (not voice now)
- dung nhieu trong deeplearning .
- Trich rut 1 doan dai va thay the tat ca bang vai cau de tom tat lai.(tom tat van ban)
- danh gia hop den, danh gia thuy tinh ( LUAN VAN: DANH GIA TINH HIEU QUA CUA HE THONG <GRASS-BOX> 
- cach tac dong cua cac tu, dong tu voi nhau rat quan trong, moi tu co gia tri ~cam xuc~.
- van pham phu thuoc phan tich ngu nghia cho ra cac quan he, huong nghien cuu hien nay. 
- dong tham chieu dai tu( I,It, That , Who , Whom).
- dung nhung ngon ngu may tinh co the hieu dc de dien ta ( toan hoc va logic)
- cay cu phap + luan ly - > lgoic to form.
- logic to form ko co ngu canh, muon co ngu canh phai o rang buoc phat ngon. 

------
			CHUONG 2:  CO SO NGON NGU VA CU PHAP TIENG ANH
-  cum dong tu rat quan trong : trong tam hanh vi, hanh dong the hien o dong tu  -> tao ra moi quan he


--------

	CHUONG 3: VAN PHAP VA PHAN TICH CU PHAP

- G0, G1, G2, G3 ( Regular) : nha toan hoc qua phan tich ngon ngu
- Cac rang buoc cua G0: P : alpha -> B 
- Cac loai van pham (o phai tren)
- Khi chung ta co cay cu phap , chung ta co dan xuat va nguoc lai 
- Dan xuat( qua trinh tao ra luan sinh) , la qua trinh tim ra cau hop hoac ko hop le voi van pham.
- Co cu phap cay <-> Dan xuat . <1>
- Qua trinh app dung lien tuc luan sinh goi la dan xuat. 
- Thuoc tinh dac biet cua van ban phi ngu canh :  <1>
- WORLD : tree-bank, ngan hang cay luan sinh .
- G3 : bat o muc tu vung (token ) ko bat o muc ngu phap. A -> aB( A,B la dai dien cho key hieu ko ket thuc, a(lowercase) ky hieu luan sinh  ket thuc.
- Regular expression.
- bieu thuc chinh qui sinh ra atomat (mo hinh toan hoc: don dinh va ko don dinh) <compiler again =))>
- Automat bo nhan dang ra cac TOKEN , cai nao la id, cai nao la letter. 
- Van pham phi nghu canh la la Push down stack (autoact
- 2pp nghien cuu TOP DOWN, Bottom up . 
- Qua trinh tim dan xuat la phai tim bang duoc ve cay , ra dc handle.
- Qua trinh tim dan xuat phai dc ( trai - phai, phai trai )
- Yeu to de qui de no cu phap .
- LL1 : ngon ngu lap trinh thuong dung
- Dung stack de luu cac lua chon khac nhau.
- kY hieu van pham xuat hien ben trai luan sinh, con lai la ky hieu ket thuc ( ben trai nhu ART, N, V, ADJ..)
